<subSubSection id="90B356A83E57819FBC54BFD546D8E770" pageId="0" pageNumber="49" type="original diagnosis">
<paragraph id="45CE067FBD5C3B7BE9CE5ACF8E26C188" pageId="0" pageNumber="49">Original diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3A503F969ADE85A01D4CBAA1CAA33F0A" pageId="0" pageNumber="49">
&quot;Pileus carnosulus, infundibuliformis, lobatus, laete ochraceus, squamulosus. Stipes solidus, pileo concolor. Lamellae confertissimae, angustissimae, furcatae, non intervenatae. Caro ochracea, sapore amaro. Sporae breviter ellipsoidae, 5,6-7 
<normalizedToken id="9CF65AB7E9102652E07CA11CAC386067" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
3,7-4,5 
<normalizedToken id="05695BC96EFA53EB0DFB291C035BDF47" originalValue="μm.”">μm.&quot;</normalizedToken>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
